Jagris didn't see anyone inside the Cybertronian Fire since she had 
arrived, giving her a chance for a little self-tour (Getting QUITE 
lost... "Other way...Stupid Navcomp..."). She was currently sitting 
in a chair in the command center, twirling like a moron, singing 'Mr. 
Roboto'.

"...Domo Arigato, Mr. Roboto... For helping me to get...Just where I 
needed to... Thank YOU!!!!..."
